query:
INSERT INTO templates (name, description, category, subcategory, thumbnailUrl, previewUrl, templateData, tags, featured, sortOrder, isPublic, createdAt, updatedAt)
VALUES 
('Vintage Memories', 'Un design vintage classique avec des filtres sépia et des bordures rétro', 'photo', 'vintage', 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Vintage+Memories', 'https://via.placeholder.com/600x600?text=Vintage+Memories', '{"width":800,"height":600,"elements":[{"type":"image","x":50,"y":50,"width":700,"height":500,"filters":{"sepia":0.8,"brightness":1.1}}]}', 'vintage,classic,sepia', 1, 1, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Modern Minimalist', 'Design épuré et moderne avec beaucoup d\'espace blanc', 'photo', 'modern', 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Modern+Minimalist', 'https://via.placeholder.com/600x600?text=Modern+Minimalist', '{"width":800,"height":600,"elements":[{"type":"image","x":100,"y":100,"width":600,"height":400,"filters":{"brightness":1.2,"contrast":1.1}}]}', 'modern,minimalist,clean', 1, 2, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Photo Book Classic', 'Mise en page classique pour livres photo avec deux colonnes', 'book', 'classic', 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Photo+Book+Classic', 'https://via.placeholder.com/600x600?text=Photo+Book+Classic', '{"pages":20,"layout":"two-column","elements":[]}', 'book,classic,layout', 1, 3, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Calendar 2025 Modern', 'Calendrier moderne avec design épuré', 'calendar', 'modern', 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Calendar+2025', 'https://via.placeholder.com/600x600?text=Calendar+2025', '{"year":2025,"type":"wall","layout":"monthly"}', 'calendar,2025,modern', 1, 4, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Custom Mug Design', 'Design personnalisé pour mug avec votre photo', 'gift', 'mug', 'https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Custom+Mug', 'https://via.placeholder.com/600x600?text=Custom+Mug', '{"itemType":"mug","size":"standard","color":"white"}', 'gift,mug,custom', 0, 5, 1, NOW(), NOW());
